        "subject": "LU-1020 llite: debug patch to track lookup_intent",
        "message": "LU-1020 llite: debug patch to track lookup_intent\n\nthe ptlrpc_request stored in lookup_intent is freed with the flag\nDISP_ENQ_OPEN_REF set at lookup_intent.d.lustre.it_disposition,\nthis patch adds the corresponding lookup_intent in ptlrpc_request\nwhile DISP_ENQ_OPEN_REF is set in it.\n\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I30a781448328cee294465a3f28a08859e6f52cc0\n"
